**Research lock (one line per product)**

- **AxiomFolio** — Golden State Warriors–style blue + gold; Sankalp’s hand mark; 4-petal + amber center is the family anchor. *(Precedent: pro-sports crest + fintech app norms.)*
- **FileFree** — TurboTax / H&R / Intuit category map is green + blue; indigo + lime counter-positions while staying "money-positive" (refund + growth) without copying incumbents.
- **LaunchFree** — LegalZoom (orange), ZenBusiness (green), Stripe Atlas (indigo) map; sky + cyan reads *launch* + *momentum* without those lanes. *(Precedent: literal sky metaphor in formation products.)*
- **Distill** — LibreTexts and standard still diagrams: vapor / condensate / essence; teal + orange encodes *refine to essence* and avoids Drake/ProSeries legacy blues. *(Precedent: textbook distillation curve + condenser imagery.)*
- **Trinkets** — Funnel to FileFree at `tools.filefree.ai`: sibling indigo; differentiation is surface + illustration density, not a new hue family. *(Precedent: sub-brand continuity in product families.)*
- **Brain** — brain.ai, Mem, Reflect, Notion AI own violet; emerald + mint = growth + custody, not "generic purple AI." *(Precedent: category color clustering in memory apps.)*
- **Paperwork Labs (parent)** — Gem clip / attachment metaphor (Notion, Slack, email affordances) with slate + single amber segment; parent mark stays neutral-ink + earned amber. *(Precedent: SaaS mark systems such as Stripe and Linear — single-stroke + one accent.)*

- **Studio** — Inherits **Azure + Amber** with AxiomFolio: internal admin = company chrome, not a separate consumer story.

